                    <span>This book provides what many others don't, which is adequate comparative examples with exposure info.  I found it complete, clearly written, and informative.  </span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">An excellent book, highly recommended.</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
